{"tid":1680191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位勇武前線，唔好再亂咁分享你啲事蹟！小心啲！","createTime":"2019-10-28T15:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T05:13:57.000Z","uid":85390,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e31c185529f7a137120a049e8b311477c16b5016","tid":1680191,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"最近聽到唔少朋友或者同事都講邊個邊個人，佢話自己係勇武或者參加過啲活動或者經歷點驚險法，但唔該你地，諗清楚先好同信任得過嘅人講，唔好亂咁分享事蹟。<br />\n<br />\n因為你咁啱唔好彩同個偽黃偽中立撚講，隨時比人篤灰。。。 除非你上前線為打卡，否則唔洗宣揚出去架，在心中啦，或者搵信任嘅人講。<br />\n<br />\n我已經聽過幾個朋友講返啲人分享嘅故事，其實佢地會無意中出賣你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以留個秘密，煲底相見啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者重光之時，每人唔同嘅經歷仲可以輯錄成書添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee986ff06167853df258724cef6b0a68f5b4e404","tid":1680191,"uid":85390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好隨便透露呀記得"},{"pid":"c89abca8a81ad176056c8b0fa102934226106a7c","tid":1680191,"uid":5995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"唔講出去人地點知我上前線呀"},{"pid":"f3ca32625868ffe02fd0d85e23ca6af86554bb2c","tid":1680191,"uid":85390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c89abca8a81ad176056c8b0fa102934226106a7c","tid":1680191,"uid":5995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"唔講出去人地點知我上前線呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"岩呀ching，你講完我都相信你無上過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c6036